                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10014" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0444</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">375 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">一颗螺丝钉都讲规矩：德胜洋楼的质量哲学与制度治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Every screw follows its rules: The quality philosophy and institutional governance of Tecsun Homes</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陆琳，马青坡，许雪美，赵雷，刘良灿</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">德胜（苏州）洋楼有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化；质量哲学；制度治理；德胜洋楼</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate culture, Philosophy of quality, Institutional governance, Values</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">德胜洋楼以“规矩治企”为核心，构建了独特的质量哲学与制度治理体系，成为现代企业伦理实践的典范。创始人聂圣哲提出“质量即人格”，将质量标准融入企业基因，通过93页《美制轻型木结构操作规程（细则）》等操作程序，确保从螺丝钉到建筑整体的品质把控。德胜洋楼以“诚实、勤劳、有爱心、不走捷径”为四维价值观，推行报销声明、保洁入职门槛、圣诞晚宴等特色实践，将抽象理念转化为员工行为准则。德胜洋楼独创“听证会制度”“1855绩效规则”等机制，以制度刚性约束行为，以文化柔性凝聚人心，实现员工离职率趋近于零、客户复购率超85%的成效。其“金色降落伞计划”、终身员工制度等举措，更将员工关怀与企业发展深度绑定。本案例通过对德胜洋楼“制度—文化—价值”的三层渗透剖析，证明规矩不仅是管理工具，更是组织信仰的载体。学生通过实际问题的分析，掌握企业文化相关理论，同时希望学生能够灵活运用相关理论，在新的时代背景下，为中国企业提供了可复制的伦理治理路径，彰显了“以文化人、以德育人”的深层力量。 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Tecsun Homes, with &quot;governing the enterprise by rules&quot; as its core, has established a unique quality philosophy and institutional governance system, becoming a model of modern enterprise ethical practice. Founder Nie Shengzhe proposed that &quot;quality is personality&quot;, integrating quality standards into the company&#39;s DNA. Through strict systems such as the 93-page &quot;Detailed Operating Procedures for American-Made Light Wood Structures&quot;, he ensures quality control from screws to the entire building. Tecsun Homes adheres to the four-dimensional values of &quot;honesty, diligence, kindness, and no shortcuts&quot;, and implements distinctive practices such as reimbursement statements, cleaning entry requirements, and Christmas banquets, transforming abstract concepts into behavioral norms for employees. Tecsun Homes has independently created mechanisms such as the &quot;Hearing System&quot; and the &quot;1855 Performance Rule&quot;, using the rigidity of systems to restrain behavior and the flexibility of culture to unite people&#39;s hearts, achieving the results of an employee turnover rate approaching zero and a customer repurchase rate exceeding 85%. Its measures such as the &quot;Golden Parachute Program&quot; and the lifetime employee system have deeply integrated employee care with the development of the enterprise. This case, through the three-level infiltration analysis of &quot;system - culture - value&quot; in Tecsun Homes, proves that rules are not only management tools but also carriers of organizational beliefs. Through the analysis of practical problems, students master the relevant theories of corporate culture. At the same time, it is hoped that students can flexibly apply these theories. In the new era background, it provides replicable ethical governance paths for Chinese enterprises and demonstrates the profound power of &quot;cultivating people through culture and educating people through virtue&quot;.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化形成动因；企业文化的功能；企业文化演变理论；企业文化四层次理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
